@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
participant "mobile-service" as MobileService
database "PostgreSQL Mobile DB" as MobileDB

Customer -> Gateway: GET /api/customers/mobiles/
Gateway -> CustomerService: GET /customers/mobiles/
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Validate JWT customer
CustomerService -> MobileService: GET /mobiles/
MobileService -> MobileDB: Query mobiles
MobileDB --> MobileService: Mobile list
MobileService --> CustomerService: Mobile list
CustomerService --> Gateway: Response JSON
Gateway --> Customer: Mobile list
@enduml
